section
  h2 Sublime keyboard shortcuts
  ul
    li Command panel: <br/><b>Ctrl + Shift + P</b> | <b>⌘ + Shift + P</b>
    li Open file: <br/><b>Ctrl + P</b> | <b>⌘ + P</b>
    li Navigate between methods: <br/><b>Ctrl + R</b> | <b>⌘ + R</b>

section
  h2 Sublime keyboard shortcuts
  ul
    li Surround with tags: <br/><b>Shift + Alt + W</b> | <b>Ctrl + Shift + W</b>
  div
    img(src="assets/raster/surround-with-tags.png")

section
  h2 Need more space?
  ul
    li Open side by side: <br/><b>Shift + Alt + [123458]</b> | <b>⌘ + ⌥ + [123458]</b> 
    li Toggle side bar: <br/><b>Ctrl + K, Ctrl + B</b> | <b>⌘ + K, ⌘ + B</b>
    li Distraction free: <br/><b>Shift + F11</b> | <b>Ctrl + Shift + ⌘ + F</b>
  img(src="assets/raster/two-columns.png")

